description:
The Duke of Normandy is the Home Secretary of the Albion Kingdom and http://anidb.net/ch88463 [Princess Charlotte]`s uncle. He handles the Kingdom`s espionage affairs and personally has hunted down potential defectors from the Kingdom, either to use them for counter-espionage against the Commonwealth`s agents or kill them outright.
Source: Wikipedia
name: Normandy-kou
